"Criminally underrated! The dialogue felt a bit sharp at points, and the story as a whole could have used some tightening, but at it's core this was a very fun ride. The heist was engaging, the stakes were clear, and the GOI itself left me wanting more. It's a very cool idea for an antagonist group. I kinda' want to play with them in some future articles."

//-- T Rutherford, on SCP-6900-D//

